This is xmppbot, an xammp or jabber bot written in C++ using gloox and boost.

=Dependecies=
- Boost 1.4.x ( tested with 1.4.7.0 and 1.4.8.0 )
- Gloox 1.0
- sqlite3
- sqlitewrapped

=Building=
Either use the supplied Code::Blocks project file or the included Makefile

=Configuration=
Either copy the example config-file in the bin/ folder, adapt it to suit your needs and start the bot with "/path/xmppbot myconfig.cfg" or use the create_basic_config.sh script to create a sqlite config ( which the bot uses as default ).
